</section>

<!-- STATS BAR -->
<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stat-item">
    <span class="stat-num">4.0★</span>
    <span class="stat-label">Google Rating</span>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <span class="stat-num">267+</span>
    <span class="stat-label">Reviews</span>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <span class="stat-num">24/7</span>
    <span class="stat-label">Open All Week</span>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <span class="stat-num">100%</span>
    <span class="stat-label">Quality Turf</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="section-tag">Our Story</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">WHERE THE CITY MEETS THE RIVER</h2>
      <p>Nestled along the scenic Buriganga riverbank in Hazaribagh, Rivershore Sports Arena offers Dhaka's most unique sports experience. Step off the busy streets into a spacious, well-maintained arena where the air feels different and the game feels bigger.</p>
      <p>Our premium futsal turf is surrounded by shaded galleries, secure lockers, and all the amenities you need to focus on what matters — playing your best game.</p>
      <a href="#booking" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:0.5rem">Book Now</a>
    </div>
    <div class="about-visual">
      <div class="about-card c1">
        <div class="about-card-icon">🏟️</div>
        <h4>Premium Indoor Futsal</h4>
        <p>High-quality artificial turf with proper field markings — designed for serious play and casual kickabouts alike.</p>
